an class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080010/extras/0c0e5ebdca6c044dd7ee64531be493bd.avif?t=1743696840\" width=600 height=90 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize your personal witch!</strong></h2>Use earned rewards to customize your witch in many different ways.<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1080010/extras/a8dfb22a8ff1c625bf810fe439ca74e5.avif?t=1743696840\" width=600 height=90 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Set new records!</strong></h2>Every second counts! Witchtastic is an exciting challenge for completionists and speedrunners.",
